asset_contract.name: Ninja Squad
asset_contract.description:
Ninja Squad is an NFT and crypto trading community with a focus on education and innovating utilities for NFTs. 

This pass will give you access to:
- A dedicated community of like-minded traders to discuss ideas, strategies, and trades
- real-time calls & analyses for NFT projects & degen plays
- cutting edge daily crypto calls
- analysis & news from our top tier crypto and NFT experts

This blog post can tell you more about our alpha channels: https://medium.com/ninja-squad/being-a-ninja-squad-member-ninja-newbie-guide-on-the-alpha-channels-d307bb0d3509

You can join our Discord community here: https://discord.com/invite/ninjasquad

When you arrive, take a moment to review our start-here channel to familiarize yourself with our channels, introduce yourselves in the alpha-ninja channel, and ask any questions you have in our help channel.

The dojo awaits you ninja!
